import { View, Text, Box, Button } from 'react-native'
import React from 'react'
import tw from "twrnc";
import Mapa from "../Imagenes/mapa.jpg"

export default function Principal() {
    return (
        <View style={tw`bg-black h-full`}>
            <View style={tw`flex-row w-full h-full bg-purple-700 justify-center items-center`}>
                {/*NAVBAR*/}
                <View style={tw`self-start flex-row h-24 w-10/12 mt-10`}>
                    <View style={tw`flex-none bg-pink-500 w-1/6 items-center justify-center rounded-bl-2xl rounded-tl-2xl`}>
                        <Text style={tw`text-xl font-bold`}>
                            ...
                        </Text>
                    </View>
                    <View style={tw`flex-1 bg-green-500 w-4/6 items-center justify-center pt-2`}>
                        <Text style={tw`text-2xl font-bold`}>
                            Unitec
                        </Text>
                    </View>
                    <View style={tw`flex-initial bg-pink-500 w-1/6 items-center justify-center rounded-br-2xl rounded-tr-2xl`}>
                        <Text style={tw`text-xl font-bold`}>
                            ...
                        </Text>
                    </View>
                </View>
                {/*FLOATING BOX*/}
                <View style={tw`flex-none w-10/12 h-3/12 bg-blue-400 mb-5 rounded-3xl self-end`}>

                </View>
            </View>

        </View>
    )
}
